snippet.title: Bombinator - Upcoming online action game
snippet.description:
Bombinator (online multiplayer | PVP arenas) is an extremely dynamic 3d action game based on cool concepts proven in legends like Bomberman, Dyna Blaster or MegaBlast. Players choose one of many available appearances in game and start to compete with each other on beautiful and challenging arenas trying to score higher and higher rank and occupying higher positions in ranking.

Want to become a beta tester subscribe at and we will inform you about upcoming beta schedule  https://bombinator.net/join-us

Join our Facebook fun page https://www.facebook.com/BombinatorGame/
